Value NEIGHBOR (\d+.\d+.\d+.\d+)
Value AS_NUMBER (\d+)
Value LINK (\S*)
Value PEER_GRP (\S+)
Value ROUTER_ID (\S+)
Value STATE (\S+)

Start
  ^BGP\s+neighbor\s+is\s+${NEIGHBOR},\s+remote\s+AS\s+${AS_NUMBER},\s+${LINK}\s+link
  ^.*peer-group\s+${PEER_GRP}
  ^.*ID\s+${ROUTER_ID}
  ^.*state\s+=\s+${STATE} -> Record
